messages.content: Hi, thank you for calling Vacatia. How can I help you today?
I'd be happy to help you with your maintenance fee. Can you please verify your phone number for me?
Thank you for verifying. Your current maintenance fee balance is $450, due on February 15th. Would you like me to send you a payment link?
I've sent the payment link to your phone number ending in 4567. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
You're welcome. Have a great day!
